nodes.text: Billy Brown is an actor who has been working in the film and gaming industry for over ten years. He is credited with voicing Master Zez-Kai Ell, Admiral Cede and additional characters in Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic II: The Sith Lords. He also voiced Chop'aa Notimo and Kleef in Star Wars: The Force Unleashed.
